Module org.microbean.development.annotation
Package org.microbean.development.annotation

Annotation Interface License

@Documented @Inherited @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({ANNOTATION_TYPE,PACKAGE,TYPE}) public @interface License
Indicates that the annotated element is governed by the license identified by the value of the uri() element.
Author:
Laird Nelson

    Required Element
